    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\nA schedule for the reading of psalms for special Shabbatot and holidays, according to <a href=\"https://mss.huc.edu/phpviewer/index.php?path=MS_453/Ms%20453_%20%2815%29.JPG\">HUC Ms. 453 fol. 15r</a>, a Seder Hazkarot Neshamot copied by Shabetai Sheftel ben Zalman Auerbach from 1730.\n</div>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" dir=\"rtl\" id=\"sortable_example\" class=\"draggable sortable\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\"><em>Festival</em></th>\n<th>Psalms</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShabbat Bereshit\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 008\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nCircumcision day\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 012\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nḤanukkah\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 030\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\n10 Tevet\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 074\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShabbat Zakhor\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 109\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nTaanit Esther\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 069\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPurim\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 022\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShushan Purim\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 060\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShabbat Parah\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 021\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShabbat haḤodesh\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 078\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShabbat haGadol\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 095\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 1 of Pesaḥ\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 105\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 2 of Pesaḥ\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 066\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 7 of Pesaḥ\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 018\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 7 of Pesaḥ\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 106\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 1 of Shavuot\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 029\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 2 of Shavuot\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 068\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\n17 Tammuz\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 079\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\n9 Av\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 137\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nRosh Ḥodesh Elul\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 047\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 1 of Rosh haShana\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 081\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 2 of Rosh haShana\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 098\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nTsom Gedalya\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 077\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShabbat Teshuva\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 032\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nErev Yom Kippur\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 107\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 1 of Sukkot\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 027\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nDay 2 of Sukkot\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 076\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nHoshana Rabba\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 085\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nShmini Atzeret\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 065\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nSimḥat Torah\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: 1px solid black; width:auto;\">\nPsalms 147\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<style>\n       .errordiv { padding:10px; margin:10px; border: 1px solid #555555;color: #000000;background-color: #f8f8f8; width:500px; }#advanced_iframe {visibility:visible;opacity:1;vertical-align:top;}.ai-info-bottom-iframe { position: fixed; z-index: 10000; bottom:0; left: 0; margin: 0px; text-align: center; width: 100%; background-color: #ff9999; padding-left: 5px;padding-bottom: 5px; border-top: 1px solid #aaa } a.ai-bold {font-weight: bold;}#ai-layer-div-advanced_iframe p {height: